stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Normal
    Normal --> FailoverInitiated : Node/Zone Failure Detected
    FailoverInitiated --> Switching : Initiating Failover
    Switching --> FailoverComplete : Failover Successful
    FailoverComplete --> Normal : Return to Normal Operation
    Switching --> FailoverFailed : Failover Unsuccessful
    FailoverFailed --> Alerting : Alert Users
    Alerting --> Normal : Issue Resolved